title._content: Waterfront Development at North Key Largo with "Plugged" Canal. Artificial Waterways May Not Exit Into the Ocean without Hard-To-Get State Permits. Developers Dig the Canals Anyway, and Buyers Can Hope That the "Plugs" Will Later Be Removed.
